{"tid":792461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手機起火爆炸　1歲女嬰嚴重燒傷","createTime":"2018-08-24T14:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T15:49:50.000Z","uid":122,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbb6c0872468743f2347fe20ec7bee687f9c0f9","tid":792461,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"中國再傳手機爆炸傷人意外。河南省周口市太康縣日前發生一起手機爆炸意外，導致一名1歲大女童雙腿嚴重燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發當時，李姓男子將自己剛買滿一年的小米手機放在地上，播放動畫影片給1歲大的女兒看，突然聽到爆炸聲，手機機身四周噴火，發生爆炸，屋內佈滿黑煙，爆炸起火導致女嬰雙腿受傷，緊急送醫後醫師鑑定為三級燒傷，目前仍在醫院接受治療，性命應可無礙。<br />\n<br />\n李男表示，這支小米手機購買剛滿一年，意外發生當時手機並不是在充電狀態，也沒有長時間使用，意外發生後已四次連絡小米公司客服，但對方僅表示會將事件呈報給上級單位，迄今沒有正式答覆。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180824/1417464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180824%2F1417464&d=sF0Pb0B18CkJn4xbHXEfCb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=894c4c7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180824%2F1417464&h=8db600b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180824/1417464</a>"},{"pid":"c3f4645d36455a9b28d62d3e35401f3f7028769d","tid":792461,"uid":114097,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"真係勁<br />\n抄到連電話爆炸都抄得咁足<br />\n利害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595aca89c522fb5d810b16edd2e3ff6913dd9e81","tid":792461,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f4645d36455a9b28d62d3e35401f3f7028769d","tid":792461,"uid":114097,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"真係勁<br />\n抄到連電話爆炸都抄得咁足<br />\n利害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB